Text: D'ya think livin' in Crowley's house got to him?
"Monkey" is one spooky song......incredible through head phones.  Better than the original.
jimmy page lived in crowley's house, not plant

Attention Robert Plant Fans:

For those that may be unaware:

One award winning Album often overlooked is "Raising Sand" by Robert Plant and Alison Krauss - It won multiple awards and Robert never sounded better.
ONG: Compare this song: "Satan Your Kingdom Must Come Down" on this album to Willie Nelson's version of the same song on his 2010 album "Country Music"!!!
